5 A BILL
6 TO BE ENTITLED
7 AN ACT
8
9 Relating to agriculture authorities; to amend Sections
10 11-20-71, 11-20-73, and 11-20-81, as last amended by Act
11 2025-301, 2025 Regular Session, Code of Alabama 1975; to
12 provide the board of directors to appoint a successor for each
13 director on the board; to allow an agriculture authority to
14 purchase goods or services through a national or regional
15 governmental cooperative purchasing program; to provide that
16 tax proceeds from the sale of alcoholic beverages collected by
17 an agriculture authority are rebated to the agriculture
18 authority; and to make nonsubstantive, technical revisions to
19 update existing code language to current style.
20 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
21 Section 1. Sections 11-20-71, 11-20-73, and 11-20-81,
22 as last amended by Act 2025-301, 2025 Regular Session, Code of
23 Alabama 1975, are amended to read as follows:
24 "§11-20-71
25 (a)(1) The board of directors of an agriculture
26 authority shall be as specified in the articles and in
27 accordance with Section 11-20-70.
28 (2) When a director vacates his or her office prior to
